abstract: With Anheuser-Busch InBev poised to auction its Central and Eastern European breweries in two weeks, private equity firms are already lining up.
snippet: With Anheuser-Busch InBev poised to auction its Central and Eastern European breweries in two weeks, private equity firms are already lining up.
lead_paragraph: With Anheuser-Busch InBev poised to auction off 11 Central and Eastern European breweries in two weeks, private equity firms are already lining up, Reuters reported, attributing the report to people familiar with the situation.
